CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 24, 2004

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2003-1048 and 2003-1049. State v. White.

Guernsey App. No. 02CA23, 2003-Ohio-2289. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellee’s motion to participate in and/or be present at oral argument,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to participate in oral argument be, and hereby is, denied.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that the motion to be present at oral argument be, and hereby is, granted.
